-- HSBC confirms Chairman Green to step down
-- 
-- Tue Sep 7, 2010 8:41am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/09/07/us-hsbc-green-idUSTRE68629920100907

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - HSBC Holdings PLC ( HSBA.L ) said on Tuesday its Group chairman Stephen Green is stepping down to become UK Minister of State for Trade and Investment. 

 Other highlights: * HSBC did not name replacement for Green, says plans to do so by end of year (London Equities Newsroom)